<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id52ec4560-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6" identifier="/us/usc/t28/s2673"><num value="2673">§ 2673.</num><heading> Reports to Congress</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The head of each federal agency shall report annually to Congress all claims paid by it under <ref href="/us/usc/t28/s2672">section 2672 of this title</ref>, stating the name of each claimant, the amount claimed, the amount awarded, and a brief description of the claim.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id52ec4561-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6">(<ref href="/us/act/1948-06-25/ch646">June 25, 1948, ch. 646</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/62/983">62 Stat. 983</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id52ec4562-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="historicalAndRevision" id="id52ec4563-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Historical and Revision Notes</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Based on title 28, U.S.C., 1940 ed., § 922 (<ref href="/us/act/1946-08-02/ch753/s404">Aug. 2, 1946, ch. 753, § 404</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/60/843">60 Stat. 843</ref>).</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Changes were made in phraseology.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id52ec4564-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="miscellaneous" id="id52ec4565-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Repeal</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/89/348/s1/1">Pub. L. 89–348, § 1(1)</ref>, <date date="1965-11-08">Nov. 8, 1965</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/79/1310">79 Stat. 1310</ref>, repealed the requirement that an annual report to Congress be made of the administrative adjustment of tort claims of $2,500 or less, stating the name of each claimant, the amount claimed, the amount awarded, and a brief description of the claim.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
